---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Community" description="A welcoming place for Rocky Horror fans, performers, and audience members connected through Golden Atlas Players.">
  <section class="hero community-hero">
    <div class="community-intro">
      <span class="badge">Community</span>
      <h1>Welcome to our community.</h1>
      <p>Rocky Horror is better when nobody has to walk in feeling like a stranger. Golden Atlas Players is building a local home for fans, performers, curious first-timers, and the beautifully over-dressed weirdos who know every callback by heart.</p>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <a class="btn" href="https://discord.gg/YFE8U3NMYV" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Join the Discord</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="https://www.facebook.com/GoldenAtlasPlayers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Follow on Facebook</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="community-embed-panel">
      <div class="facebook-embed">
        <iframe
          title="Golden Atlas Players Facebook page"
          src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/page.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGoldenAtlasPlayers&tabs=timeline&width=500&height=600&small_header=false&adapt_container_width=true&hide_cover=false&show_facepile=true"
          width="500"
          height="600"
          style="border:none;overflow:hidden"
          scrolling="no"
          frameborder="0"
          allowfullscreen="true"
          allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="two-col">
    <div>
      <h2 class="section-title">New here?</h2>
      <p class="section-copy">You do not need to know every callback, dress perfectly, or already know someone. If you’re curious, nervous, or just want to see what this crowd is about, come by, ask questions, and take it at your own pace.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card">
      <h3>Want to get involved?</h3>
      <p class="section-copy">We’re always interested in audience energy, shadowcast interest, tech and backstage help, flyers and outreach, and people who want to help the community feel welcoming.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Community expectations</h2>
    <ul class="list">
      <li>Be kind.</li>
      <li>Respect consent and boundaries.</li>
      <li>Help new people feel welcome.</li>
      <li>Keep the weird fun, not uncomfortable.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Join the Discord</h2>
    <p class="section-copy">For ongoing chat, fan conversation, planning, and connecting between shows.</p>
    <div class="btn-row">
      <a class="btn" href="https://discord.gg/YFE8U3NMYV" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Join the Discord</a>
    </div>
    <div class="discord-widget-wrap">
      <iframe
        src="https://discordapp.com/widget?id=1520898461359145070&theme=dark"
        width="350"
        height="500"
        allowtransparency="true"
        frameborder="0"
        sandbox="allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    align-items: center;
  }

  .community-hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .community-intro {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .community-embed-panel {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .facebook-embed {
    max-width: 500px;
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(217, 45, 45, 0.24);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .facebook-embed iframe {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 500px;
    border: 0;
  }

  .discord-widget-wrap {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    display: inline-block;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(217, 45, 45, 0.24);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .discord-widget-wrap iframe {
    display: block;
    border: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .community-hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .two-col {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
